QuestData.Title: Ready the Air Force
QuestData.Description: I gave Hellscream my personal guarantee that I'd have his airfleet ready this week, but our flagship - The Spear of Durotar - still doesn't have its primary engines installed.$B$BFleep promised me a dangerously shiny new engine last week. Go to her junkyard behind the bank and find out what the holdup is.$B$BThe airfleet is waiting on us, $n!
QuestData.LogDescription: Look for Fleep at her junkyard within Bilgewater Harbor in Azshara.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Look for Fleep at her junkyard within Bilgewater Harbor in Azshara.
QuestData.RewardText: <Fleep wipes her face, plastering an enormous grease smear across her cheek.>$B$BWhat? The Captain said WHAT?$B$B<She shakes her pipe wrench threateningly.>$B$BIt's HIS fault this big beast of an engine is delayed.
